movie.title: Selena
movie.description_intro: The film tells the story of the life of Mexican "Tejano" style singer Selena Quintanilla-Perez and the progress of her career resulting in her No. 1 US album.

movies.title: The Ultimate Warrior
movies.summary: Only a few people still live in New York City in 2012. They are organized in gangs with their own turfs. One of them is led by Baron, another one by Carrot, and they are constantly at war with each other. Baron's gang is more peaceful and have developed seeds that can germinate despite the virus plague. The lone ranger Carson is hired by Bishop for protection.

movies.title: Children Shouldn't Play with Dead Things
movies.title_english: Children Shouldn't Play with Dead Things
movies.title_long: Children Shouldn't Play with Dead Things (1972)
movies.summary: An acting troupe led by Alan Ormsby go to a graveyard on a remote island to perform a necromantic ritual. The ritual works too well and soon the dead are walking about and chowing down on human flesh. The dwindling group of survivors struggle to escape.

movies.title: The Millionaires' Express
movies.summary: Multi-genre flick (western, martial arts, comedy, adventure, etc.) with an all-star cast about a man who returns to his home town, buys everything in sight, and tries to improve its municipal (and his personal) profits by sabotaging a train so the passengers all have to stop in his town and spend lots o' money! Throw in various subplots involving some Japanese swordsmen, some bungling bankrobbers (one of whom is the head of security), and a gang of no-goods who try to mess up the town.

movies.title: Route Irish
movies.summary: The story of a private security contractor in Iraq who rejected the official explanation of his friend's death and sets out to discover the truth.
